                <p style="font-size:30px;padding-top:40px;font-weight:bold" align="center">
                  CONTRAT DE TRAVAIL A DUREE DETERMINEE
                </p>
                <div style="width:30%;border-top:1px solid;margin-top:-30px;margin-left:35%"></div>
                <p style="font-size:25px;height:50px;margin-top:100px;font-weight:bold" align="left">
